<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 29 - 33. ♀ genitalia of Pyralis spp. 29. P. cardinalis, GPBW 7939, Belgorod obl., Borisovka.; 30. P. regalis, GPBW 7941, Slovenia, Granska Gora. 31. P. sagarrai, GPBW 8151, France, Pyrenees or., Olette. 32. P. kacheticalis (Christoph), L. Kaila prep. 6305, Lebanon, Koura. 33. P. perversalis (Herrich-Schaeffer), GPBW 8403, S. Ural, Cheliabinsk oblast." , "Figures 22 - 24. ♂ genitalia of Pyralis spp. 22. P. cardinalis sp. nov., GPBW 7913, Belgorod oblast, Makeshino Stenki. 23. P. regalis ([Denis & Schiffermueller]), GPBW 7908, France, Corse, Patrimonio. 24. P. sagarrai Leraut, GPBW 8148, France, Pyrenees or., Olette." , "Figures 4 - 11. Pyralis sp., habitus. 4 - 7. P. cardinalis sp. nov., 4. ♂, Finland, V, Kemioensaari, leg. J. Tyllinen. 5. ♀, A, Lemland, leg. B. Wikstroem & K. Vaalamo; 6. ♂, Finland, U, Kirkkonummi, leg. J. Junnilainen; 7. ♂, Finland, U, Raasepori, leg. L. Kaila. 8 - 11. P. regalis. 8. ♂, Greece, Lesvos, leg. L. Kaila & J. Kullberg. 9. ♀, Slovenia, Granska Gora, leg. B. Wikstroem; 10. ♂, Italy, Tuscany, Cortona, leg. B. Wikstroem. 11. Bulgaria, 5 km S. Blagoevgrad, ♀, leg. B. A. Bengtsson." , "Figure 2. Pyralis cardinalis sp. nov., holotype, ♂, habitus." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/473655" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/473652" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/473649" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/473647" .

